DETAILS AND INSTRUCTION FOR EXAM
1. The student may not use his or her textbook, course notes, or any help from students near by, If any student found doing any of these activity can result in Cancilatin of exam.
2. Students must attempt all questions as there is no negative marks questions.
3. For each questions there is 1 Min. If timer hits zero then exam will finished itself and result will shown on the screen and saved too. If you want to finish exam by your own before time then You should go to last question then you will find the finish button but till exam ends you have to wait.
